---
import Icon from '@/shared/components/Icon.astro'
---

<section class='process' id='process'>
  <div class='wrapper'>
    <div class='process-header' data-aos='fade-up'>
      <span class='process-label'>Implementación</span>
      <h2 class='process-title'>
        Adopta el ecosistema en <span>4 pasos</span>
      </h2>
      <p class='process-subtitle'>
        Un proceso de migración simple, transparente y acompañado. Trabajamos contigo para que pases
        al siguiente nivel digital.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class='process-timeline'>
      <div class='process-line'></div>

      <div class='process-step' data-aos='fade-up' data-aos-delay='100'>
        <div class='process-step-number'>
          <span>01</span>
        </div>
        <div class='process-step-content'>
          <div class='process-step-tag'>Paso 1</div>
          <h3 class='process-step-title'>Consultoría Inicial</h3>
          <p class='process-step-text'>
            Entendemos cómo funciona tu negocio actualmente. Analizamos tus cuellos de botella y te
            mostramos exactamente cómo el ecosistema Gadmin puede ayudarte.
          </p>
          <div class='process-step-deliverables'>
            <span class='process-deliverable'
              ><Icon name='document-text' size={16} /> Diagnóstico de tu negocio</span
            >
            <span class='process-deliverable'
              ><Icon name='check-circle' size={16} /> Plan de acción personalizado</span
            >
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class='process-step' data-aos='fade-up' data-aos-delay='200'>
        <div class='process-step-number'>
          <span>02</span>
        </div>
        <div class='process-step-content'>
          <div class='process-step-tag'>Paso 2</div>
          <h3 class='process-step-title'>Configuración & Migración</h3>
          <p class='process-step-text'>
            Te ayudamos a configurar tu cuenta, importar tus productos y clientes actuales. Dejamos
            todo listo para que empieces a trabajar de inmediato.
          </p>
          <div class='process-step-deliverables'>
            <span class='process-deliverable'
              ><Icon name='arrow-path' size={16} /> Migración de datos</span
            >
            <span class='process-deliverable'
              ><Icon name='cog-6-tooth' size={16} /> Configuración de cuenta</span
            >
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class='process-step' data-aos='fade-up' data-aos-delay='300'>
        <div class='process-step-number'>
          <span>03</span>
        </div>
        <div class='process-step-content'>
          <div class='process-step-tag'>Paso 3</div>
          <h3 class='process-step-title'>Capacitación</h3>
          <p class='process-step-text'>
            Te enseñamos a ti y a tu equipo cómo sacarle el máximo provecho a nuestras aplicaciones.
            Resolvemos todas las dudas antes del lanzamiento final.
          </p>
          <div class='process-step-deliverables'>
            <span class='process-deliverable'
              ><Icon name='user' size={16} /> Entrenamientos guiados</span
            >
            <span class='process-deliverable'
              ><Icon name='light-bulb' size={16} /> Tutoriales en video</span
            >
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class='process-step' data-aos='fade-up' data-aos-delay='400'>
        <div class='process-step-number'>
          <span>04</span>
        </div>
        <div class='process-step-content'>
          <div class='process-step-tag'>Post-Migración</div>
          <h3 class='process-step-title'>Crecimiento & Soporte</h3>
          <p class='process-step-text'>
            Tu negocio ahora cuenta con tecnología de primer nivel. Seguimos contigo mediante
            soporte continuo y lanzamientos de nuevas funcionalidades basadas en tus comentarios.
          </p>
          <div class='process-step-deliverables'>
            <span class='process-deliverable'
              ><Icon name='rocket-launch' size={16} /> Nuevos lanzamientos</span
            >
            <span class='process-deliverable'
              ><Icon name='chat-bubble-oval-left' size={16} /> Soporte humano activo</span
            >
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .process {
    padding: 6rem 1rem;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, #f5f0f0 0%, var(--neutral-02) 50%, #f5f0f0 100%);
    position: relative;
  }

  .process-header {
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 650px;
    margin: 0 auto 4rem;
  }

  .process-label {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 0.3rem 1rem;
    border-radius: 999px;
    background: rgba(77, 93, 239, 0.06);
    border: 1px solid rgba(77, 93, 239, 0.15);
    color: var(--primary);
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  }

  .process-title {
    font-size: var(--48-pt);
    font-weight: 800;
    color: var(--shade-03);
    margin: 0 0 1rem;
    line-height: 1.15;
  }

  .process-title span {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary), var(--shade-03));
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
  }

  .process-subtitle {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: var(--shade-04);
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin: 0;
    font-weight: 400;
  }

  .process-timeline {
    position: relative;
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .process-line {
    position: absolute;
    left: 32px;
    top: 0;
    bottom: 0;
    width: 2px;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--primary), var(--shade-03));
    opacity: 0.2;
    border-radius: 2px;
  }

  .process-step {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    align-items: flex-start;
    position: relative;
  }

  .process-step-number {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    width: 64px;
    height: 64px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary), var(--shade-03));
    box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(77, 93, 239, 0.25);
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .process-step-number span {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: var(--white);
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
  }

  .process-step-content {
    background: white;
    border-radius: 1rem;
    padding: 1.75rem 2rem;
    border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06);
    flex: 1;
    transition:
      transform 0.3s ease,
      box-shadow 0.3s ease;
  }

  .process-step-content:hover {
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06);
  }

  .process-step-tag {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 0.2rem 0.6rem;
    border-radius: 999px;
    background: rgba(77, 93, 239, 0.06);
    color: var(--primary);
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .process-step-title {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--shade-03);
    margin: 0 0 0.5rem;
  }

  .process-step-text {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: var(--shade-04);
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin: 0 0 1rem;
    font-weight: 400;
  }

  .process-step-deliverables {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 0.5rem;
  }

  .process-deliverable {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.25rem;
    padding: 0.3rem 0.7rem;
    border-radius: 0.5rem;
    background: rgba(77, 93, 239, 0.04);
    border: 1px solid rgba(77, 93, 239, 0.08);
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: var(--shade-04);
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  @media screen and (max-width: 768px) {
    .process {
      padding: 4rem 1rem;
    }

    .process-title {
      font-size: var(--40-pt);
    }

    .process-line {
      left: 24px;
    }

    .process-step-number {
      width: 48px;
      height: 48px;
    }

    .process-step-number span {
      font-size: 0.9rem;
    }

    .process-step-content {
      padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem;
    }

    .process-step {
      gap: 1rem;
    }

    .process-step-deliverables {
      flex-direction: column;
    }
  }
</style>
